title: $:/plugins/codemirror5/codemirror-fullscreen/readme

This plugin adds a ''Fullscreen editing Mode'' to the [[CodeMirror|http://codemirror.net]] text editor. It needs the latest [[CodeMirror plugin|$:/plugins/codemirror5/codemirror]] to be installed

Pressing ''F11'' with the focus within the editor-textarea will make the editor go fullscreen, pressing ''F11'' again leaves fullscreen-mode

